-End Sub
-
-'Set all as per ball position & speed.
-
-Sub PlaySoundAtBall(soundname)
-  PlaySoundAt soundname, ActiveBall
-End Sub
-
-'Set position as table object and Vol manually.
-
-Sub PlaySoundAtVol(sound, tableobj, Volume)
